name: In Bloom
description:
In Bloom

Original Fine art print

The Print measures 8.75 x 8.75 inches with white border for framing. Image is about 7.5".

The back is signed and titled.

Professionally printed locally here in Philadelphia on Hahnemuhle Photo Rag (%100 cotton) using archival pigment inks.

Also available in 4x4" ($10).
